   <td colspan="4" class="content">
    <pre>Hey Jessica,

I'm reading the code, and just tested the forwarder for my own user account now. 
That seems to work fine.

I did notice that the forwarder addresses expire after 3-5 days (depending on 
when in the lifecycle of a forwarder you see the message).

Do you think it's possible/probable that you waited this long, and that's why 
the reply-all didn't work?

We do that, for what it's worth, to avoid spam-harvesting bots harvesting these 
email addresses and then sending lots of spam to OpenHatch users through our 
forwarder. One thing I am totally OK trying is doubling the lifespan of these 
forwarders.

Curious if you can provide further input. Thanks for raising the issue, and 
sorry it took me a bit to respond effectively.</pre>
   </td>
  </tr>
 
 
